  "comment": "Fuze610Z LED Wash Moving Head with Zoom: The Fuze610Z is powered by 6x 10W RGBW 4-IN-1 colour LEDs and is equipped with motorised zoom allowing for a variable beam angle from 2°- 24°. With the high-quality optics it’s also possible to combine all six light beams into one big, fat beam. Exact positioning is possible through 16-bit movement resolution (540-degree pan and 180-degree tilt). The fixture is designed in a compact housing and is ideal for lighting designers, DJs, bands, clubs, bars and installations where small footprint and low weight is critical. It can be controlled by DMX, with sound activation or used in standalone mode with the Master/Slave function.\n\n",
